title: Michael Golden's G.I. Joe Yearbook - Artist's Edition Portfolio
description:
English | CBZ | 47 Pages

Michael Golden's G.I. Joe Yearbook: Artist's Edition Portfolio
Publisher:  IDW Publishing
Publication Date:  February 2013

Writer:  Larry Hama
Art and Cover:  Michael Golden

Originally published in G.I. Joe Yearbook #2 by Marvel Comics.  From the people who bring you the Eisner Award-winning Artist's Edition series, comes the next Artist's Edition portfolio: the legendary G.I. JOE Year Book #2 by Michael Golden. The cover and all 22 interior pages are all presented here on individual pages that mimic Golden's gorgeous original art. And, remember, this is a HARDCOVER portfolio-like the Neal Adams Thrillkill and Bernie Wrightson Much Monster portfolios before it-and matches the exacting quality of all previous Artist's Editions.

Thanks goes to Lusiphur for this release.
